                                  Press Enter to create "<span x-text="tagInput"></span>"
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                            <span>Start typing for suggestions, or press Enter/comma to add tags. These help organize and categorize your timeline.</span>
                          </div>
